              </p>
              <p class="text-foreground/60 text-sm italic">
                Peru's famous Cuy, served Amanto style. Accompanied with mortared potatoes topped with an elderberry 
                glaze, and creole salad.
              </p>
            </div>
          </BackgroundGradient>

          <BackgroundGradient className="p-8">
